                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>Secretary of State <persName corresp="#p_ADG1">Acheson</persName> was Chairman of
                    the United States Delegation to the Seventh Session of the United Nations
                    General <pb facs="0868" n="822" xml:id="pg_822"/> Assembly, which opened in New
                    York on October 14, 1952. On October 16, he spoke to the General Assembly in an
                    address entitled “Achieving the Goals of the Charter.” His speech is printed in
                    the Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, October 27, 1952, pages
                    639–645.</p>
            </div>
